videos.description: North Carolina's Isaiah Hicks throws down a baseline dunk early in the first half against Syracuse.
videos.headline: UNC's Hicks throws down early slam

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyler Lydon is left wide open for an easy 3-pointer in the first half against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Cuse drains easy 3-pointer

videos.description: Kenny Williams sends the ball up to Theo Pinson in transition for a second-half dunk against Syracuse.

videos.description: Justin Jackson runs the length of the court and puts up a tough shot and-1 in the second half against Syracuse.
videos.headline: UNC's Jackson drains tough lay-in
